hilst visiting are as we intended it to be none of the cookies used on our website will collect information that will personally identify you at santander consumer finance we use cookies in the following ways to track how visitors reach our site and the path they take through it to help us improve our service to you for example we use google analytics a popular web analytics service provided by google google analytics uses cookies to help us to analyse how users use the site find our more about how these cookies are used on the google privacy site to monitor and manage our website traffic to understand how our advertising campaigns and promotions within the santander consumer finance website are working to improve our site design offers and promotions none of the cookies used on our website will collect information that will personally identify you and no information is passed to third parties two types of cookies are used on this website session cookies these are temporary cookies which only exist in the period you access the website or more strictly until you close the browser after accessing the website session cookies help the santander website remember what you chose on the previous page therefore avoiding having to reenter information on our website these cookies do not contain personal information and cannot be used to identify you persistent cookies these are cookies which remain on your device after you have visited our website these cookies help us identify you as a unique visitor by storing a randomly generated number the length of time a cookie will remain on your device will depend on the type of cookie on our website these cookies do not contain personal information and cannot be used to identify you how to control and delete cookies santander consumer finance will not use cookies to collect personally identifiable information about you however if you wish to restrict or block the cookies which are set by us or indeed any other website you can do this through your browser settings the help function within your browser should tell you how alternatively you may wish to visit wwwaboutcookiesorg which contains comprehensive information on how to do this on a wide variety of browsers you will also find details on how to delete cookies from your computer including those from this visit as well as more general information about cookies for information on how to do this on the browser of your mobile device you will need to refer to your handset manual about us  find out more about santander  santander uk click if you do not want to see this message again santander uses cookies to deliver superior functionality and to enhance your experience of our websites read about how we use cookies and how you can control them here continued use of this site indicates that you accept this policy close navigation you are in about santander uk about us santander uk announces half year  results key highlights full details of santander uks half year results click here you may also be interested in  of  close you may also be interested in titulo lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit ipsum dolor sit  of  santander uk plc registered office  triton square regents place london nw an united kingdom registered number  registered in england and wales wwwsantandercouk telephone    calls may be recorded or monitored authorised by the prudential regulation authority and regulated by the financial conduct authority and the prudential regulation authority our financial services register number is  you can check this on the financial services register by visiting the fca’s website wwwfcaorgukregister santander and the flame logo are registered trademarks santander uk plc  united kingdom  duedil search for a company or director sign insign inproductteamscustomersplansaboutinternationalbloghelptalk to sales    product teams customers plans about contact duedil santander uk plc gbactiverep